### ======================================================
### LINE Webhook & Health 手動測試（公版）
###
### 使用方式：
###   1. 複製整個 customers/_template/ 到 customers/{tenant}/
###   2. 將 @baseUrlProd / @baseUrlStaging 改為該客戶的 Function App URL
###   3. 填入 @lineChannelSecret 與 @testUserId
###
### 簽章產生方式（X-Line-Signature）：
###   BODY='<json body 原始字串>'
###   SIG=$(echo -n "$BODY" | openssl dgst -sha256 -hmac "$LINE_CHANNEL_SECRET" -binary | base64)
###   echo "X-Line-Signature: $SIG"
### ======================================================

@baseUrlProd    = https://{tenant}-func.azurewebsites.net/api
@baseUrlStaging = https://{tenant}-func-staging.azurewebsites.net/api
@baseUrl        = {{baseUrlProd}}

@lineChannelSecret = YOUR_LINE_CHANNEL_SECRET
@testUserId        = Uxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Health Check
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check - Production
GET {{baseUrlProd}}/health

### Health Check - Staging
GET {{baseUrlStaging}}/health

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 2. Webhook 連通測試（空事件陣列）
#    ⚠️ 需要填入正確的 X-Line-Signature，否則回傳 401
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Webhook Verify（空事件 - 模擬 LINE Verify 按鈕）
POST {{baseUrl}}/LineWebhook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Line-Signature: REPLACE_WITH_VALID_SIGNATURE

{
  "destination": "Utest123",
  "events": []
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 3. 模擬真實 LINE 訊息事件
#    ⚠️ 需要有效 X-Line-Signature
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### 模擬用戶傳送文字訊息（需有效 signature）
POST {{baseUrl}}/LineWebhook
Content-Type: application/json
X-Line-Signature: REPLACE_WITH_VALID_SIGNATURE

{
  "destination": "Utest123",
  "events": [
    {
      "type": "message",
      "message": {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "999999999",
        "text": "你好，請問幾天到貨？"
      },
      "webhookEventId": "test-event-001",
      "deliveryContext": { "isRedelivery": false },
      "timestamp": 1708502400000,
      "source": {
        "type": "user",
        "userId": "{{testUserId}}"
      },
      "replyToken": "EXPIRED_REPLY_TOKEN_WILL_FALLBACK_TO_PUSH",
      "mode": "active"
    }
  ]
}
